---

<BaseLayout
  title="Company Formation in Saudi | Start a New Business in Saudi"
  description="Make your Company Formation in Saudi easy with Indexauh. The best Business Set Up Agency with 25 years of experience helping you start your company smoothly."
>
<style>
  .sec-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .idx-pill { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.28); color: #fff; font-size: 0.78rem; padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 9999px; font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; }
  .idx-form input, .idx-form select, .idx-form textarea { width: 100%; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 11px 14px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #374151; outline: none; font-family: inherit; background: #fff; box-sizing: border-box; }
  .idx-form input:focus, .idx-form select:focus, .idx-form textarea:focus { border-color: #38B2AC; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(56,178,172,0.15); }
  .idx-form textarea { resize: none; }
  .idx-submit { width: 100%; background: #2D3748; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; padding: 13px; border-radius: 10px; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.95rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .idx-submit:hover { background: #1A202C; }
  .company-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #eef0f6; border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; transition: all 0.25s; }
  .company-card:hover { border-color: #B2F5EA; box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(56,178,172,0.08); }
  .benefit-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px; }
  .faq-item { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
  .faq-q { width: 100%; background: #fff; border: none; text-align: left; padding: 18px 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1A202C; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .faq-a { padding: 0 20px; max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.2s; }
  .faq-a.open { max-height: 300px; padding: 0 20px 16px; }
  .faq-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .faq-item.open .faq-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); }
  @media(max-width:768px){
    .hero-title { font-size: 2rem !important; }
    .split-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 32px !important; }
    .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .three-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .four-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr  !important; }
  }
</style>

<!-- ════════════ HERO ════════════ -->
<section style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:500px;display:flex;align-items:center;">
  <img
    src="/images/img-47.webp"
    alt="Company Formation in Saudi Arabia"
    style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 40%;display:block;"
  />
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(26,32,44,0.92) 0%,rgba(45,55,72,0.80) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(56,178,172,0.18) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:28px 28px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>

  <div class="sec-inner" style="max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;padding:96px 24px;text-align:center;width:100%;">
    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:18px;">
      <span class="idx-pill">Convenient</span>
      <span class="idx-pill">Budget-Friendly</span>
      <span class="idx-pill">25+ Yrs Experience</span>
      <span class="idx-pill">Genuine</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.2rem);font-weight:900;color:#fff;line-height:1.15;margin:0 0 20px;">
      COMPANY FORMATION<br/>IN SAUDI ARABIA
    </h1>
    <p style="color:#B2F5EA;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.8;margin:0 auto 32px;max-width:680px;">
      Setting up a company in Saudi Arabia offers several advantages due to the country's business-friendly environment and numerous opportunities for growth. If you are looking for a business consultant, we at Index are ready to serve you.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="#get-in-touch" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#38B2AC;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:9999px;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(56,178,172,0.4);">Get Free Consultation &rarr;</a>
      <a href="#details" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);color:#fff;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:9999px;text-decoration:none;">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════ WHY FORM IN SAUDI ARABIA ════ -->
<section id="details" style="background:#fff;padding:76px 24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,transparent,transparent 48px,rgba(56,178,172,0.04) 48px,rgba(56,178,172,0.04) 49px);pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>

  <div class="sec-inner split-grid" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr;gap:52px;align-items:center;">
    <div>
      <p style="color:#2D3748;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:0.75rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px;">
        <span style="display:inline-block;width:28px;height:1px;background:#2D3748;"></span>Overview
      </p>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3vw,2.2rem);font-weight:900;color:#1A202C;line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 18px;">Why Consider Company Formation in Saudi Arabia?</h2>
      <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:20px;">
        Here are some reasons to consider setting up your business in Saudi Arabia:
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">
        {formationReasons.map(r => (
          <div style="background:#F8FAFF;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-left:3px solid #38B2AC;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;">
            <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:#1A202C;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 4px;">{r.title}</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.98rem;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">{r.body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div style="position:relative;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);">
        <img src="/images/saudi-flag.webp" alt="Company formation Saudi Arabia" style="width:100%;height:440px;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
        <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,transparent 50%,rgba(26,32,44,0.72) 100%);"></div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:20px;right:20px;">
          <p style="color:#fff;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 4px;">Professional Company Formation in Saudi Arabia</p>
          <p style="color:#B2F5EA;font-size:0.75rem;margin:0;">End-to-end support by Index Office Services</p>
        </div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:80px;left:-14px;background:#2D3748;color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:10px;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
          2500+ Companies Formed
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════ SECTORS, TYPES & PROCEDURES ════ -->
<section style="background:#F8FAFF;padding:76px 24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(45,55,72,0.02) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(45,55,72,0.02) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>

  <div class="sec-inner" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">

    <!-- Banner image header -->
    <div style="position:relative;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);margin-bottom:52px;">
      <img src="/images/img-41.webp" alt="Saudi Arabia business setup" style="width:100%;height:220px;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 35%;display:block;" />
      <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(26,32,44,0.88) 0%,rgba(26,32,44,0.5) 55%,transparent 100%);"></div>
      <div style="position:absolute;top:50%;left:40px;transform:translateY(-50%);">
        <p style="color:#38B2AC;font-weight:700;font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 6px;">Setup Guide</p>
        <h2 style="color:#fff;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.5vw,2rem);font-weight:900;margin:0;max-width:500px;line-height:1.25;">Types, Sectors & Procedures for Company Formation in Saudi Arabia</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Types & Sectors side by side -->
    <div class="two-col" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px;margin-bottom:32px;">

      <!-- Company types -->
      <div class="company-card">
        <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 16px;border-left:3px solid #38B2AC;padding-left:10px;">Types of Companies in Saudi Arabia</h3>
        <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;">
          {companyTypes.map(t => (
            <li style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:1rem;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.6;">
              <span style="width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:#38B2AC;flex-shrink:0;"></span>
              {t.title}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Promising sectors -->
      <div class="company-card">
        <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 16px;border-left:3px solid #38B2AC;padding-left:10px;">Promising Sectors for New Business Setup in Saudi Arabia</h3>
        <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;">
          {promisingSectors.map(s => (
            <li style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:1rem;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.6;">
              <span style="width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:#38B2AC;flex-shrink:0;"></span>
              {s}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Procedures -->
    <div class="company-card">
      <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 16px;border-left:3px solid #38B2AC;padding-left:10px;">Procedures for Forming a Company in Saudi Arabia</h3>
      <ol style="padding-left:18px;margin:0;color:#4B5563;font-size:1rem;line-height:2.1;">
        <li><strong>Determine Business Activity:</strong> Identify the type of business activity and legal structure suitable for your company.</li>
        <li><strong>Choose a Business Name:</strong> Select a unique name for your company and ensure it complies with the regulations.</li>
        <li><strong>Draft Articles of Association:</strong> Prepare the legal documents outlining the company's structure, shareholding, and operations.</li>
        <li><strong>Capital Requirement:</strong> Deposit the required share capital in a bank account in Saudi Arabia.</li>
        <li><strong>Obtain Approvals and Licenses:</strong> Obtain necessary approvals and licenses from relevant government authorities, such as the Ministry of Commerce, SAGIA, and other sector-specific regulators.</li>
        <li><strong>Commercial Registration:</strong> Register the company with the Ministry of Commerce and obtain a commercial registration (CR) certificate.</li>
        <li><strong>Municipal License:</strong> Obtain a license from the municipality in the specific region where the company will operate.</li>
        <li><strong>Hire Employees and Obtain Visas:</strong> Recruit employees and apply for the required visas and work permits.</li>
      </ol>
      <div style="background:#F0FFFE;border:1px solid #B2F5EA;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;margin-top:16px;">
        <p style="font-size:0.98rem;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">
          Before that, you need to consider the following legal requirements such as foreign investment regulations, employment laws, ownership restrictions, and much more. We can help you with all the formalities and procedures. We can even help you find the right people for your partnership in company formation in Saudi Arabia.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

